Note on bundled sample libraries (instruments/LL, instruments/SB, instruments/90):

The factory sample WAVs distributed with this repository are community-
archived Mellotron source recordings circulated freely for personal use.
They are NOT licensed under MIT and are NOT redistributable for commercial
purposes. Their original recordings remain the property of their respective
sources. If you intend to redistribute the WAVs or use them in a commercial
release, verify usage rights with the original archive maintainers first.

The MIT licence above applies to the Mello plugin code (src/, scripts/,
module.json, README.md, design-spec.md, CLAUDE.md) — NOT to the contents of
instruments/.
